		<node ID="ID_1486501026" LINK="http://wps.prenhall.com/ecs_park_fee_2/87/22279/5703574.cw/index.html" TEXT="Chapter 1 - Engineering Economic Decisions">
			<node ID="ID_1047815989" TEXT="The term engineering economic decision refers to all investment decisions relating to engineering projects. The most interesting facet of an economic decision from an engineer&#8217;s point of view is the evaluation of costs and benefits associated with making a capital investment." />
