		<node ID="ID_1511989344" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Engineering_economics" TEXT="Engineering economics - Wikipedia">
			<node ID="ID_1126608173" TEXT="Fundamentally engineering economics involves formulating estimating and evaluating the economic outcomes when alternatives to accomplish a defined purpose are available. In some U.S. undergraduate civil engineering curricula engineering economics is a required course." />
